# Scenario 4 — Incorrect Network Interface

## Symptom

* Network config applied but no connectivity

## Cause

* Wrong interface name (e.g. `eth0` instead of `ens18`)

## Impact

* Host becomes unreachable after netplan apply

## Resolution

```bash
ip a
```

* Update `interface_name` in `host_vars`

## Prevention

* Always validate interface before applying config
* Consider dynamic detection (future improvement)

