# Scenario 5 — SSH Sent to HTTP Port

## Error

```bash
Invalid character found in method name [SSH-2.0-libssh2...]
```

## Cause

* SSH client connected to HTTP service (wrong port)

## Impact

* Connection failure
* Misleading error message

## Resolution

* Verify correct port and service

## Prevention

* Validate:

  * Target IP
  * Port (22 vs 80/443)
  * Service availability

